<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB07854</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT MANDATING EVERY GOVERNMENT AND PRIVATE ESTABLISHMENT TO PROVIDE FREE POTABLE WATER IN ALL THEIR EDIFICES AND OFFICES FOR THEIR PATRONS</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Provides for a clean water refilling station in every edifice and office of every government and private establishment to supply free potable drinking water to their patrons; Aims to reduce the use of single-use plastic bottles that are nocuous to ecological balance

